Package com.intellij.debugger.engine.evaluation.expression

Class CaptureTraverser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.debugger.engine.evaluation.expression.CaptureTraverser

  • public final class CaptureTraverser
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class to find a value of captured outer class "this" object (probably several levels higher from the current class)

      • traverse

        public com.sun.jdi.ObjectReference traverse(com.sun.jdi.ObjectReference objRef)
        Looks for a captured outer this having inner this
        Parameters:
        objRef - an inner this object
        Returns:
        a reference to the outer class instance, or null if not found or this traverser is not valid. Direct traverser simply return the argument.

                                      PsiClass fromClass,

        Creates a traverser that is capable to find an instance of the targetClass having a reference to the fromClass instance
        Parameters:
        targetClass - target (outer) class
        fromClass - source (inner) class
        checkInheritance - if true, inheritors of target class are also acceptable
        Returns:
        a traverser capable to find an instance of the targetClass
